105
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:27,750
There are two more people, who I will meet soon.

106
00:05:29,125 --> 00:05:32,792
That means we still don't know
where the other seven are.

107
00:05:35,875 --> 00:05:41,208
Although I didn't want to tell you,
four of them are dead.

108
00:05:42,583 --> 00:05:47,542
The other three are alive,
but they're in states which can't be helped.

109
00:05:47,542 --> 00:05:50,458
What are states that can't be helped?

110
00:05:50,458 --> 00:05:52,208
It's a secret.

111
00:05:53,958 --> 00:05:56,542
We're asking you seriously.

112
00:05:57,708 --> 00:06:01,333
I'm also keeping a secret seriously.

113
00:06:01,333 --> 00:06:02,500
I don't get what you mean.

114
00:06:02,500 --> 00:06:04,375
Kana... Katia.

115
00:06:04,375 --> 00:06:05,917
To find so many students

116
00:06:05,917 --> 00:06:09,792
in such a huge world must be very tough.

117
00:06:10,958 --> 00:06:15,417
You're doing this for all of us.

118
00:06:16,417 --> 00:06:18,833
It's the duty of a teacher.

119
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:21,542
Besides, most of the students
are in humans' area

120
00:06:21,542 --> 00:06:24,208
and were found as humans.

121
00:06:24,208 --> 00:06:27,083
It's not as tough as you said.

122
00:06:27,083 --> 00:06:30,792
There are very few exceptions like me.

123
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:34,833
You can't help the other three...

124
00:06:34,833 --> 00:06:36,875
It's a secret.

125
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:46,167
You will find out one day, but not today.

126
00:06:46,167 --> 00:06:47,458
I get it.

127
00:06:47,458 --> 00:06:49,125
By the way, let me give you an advice.

128
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:50,458
Advice?

129
00:06:50,458 --> 00:06:52,875
Try not to practise any skill.

130
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:54,333
Why?

131
00:06:54,333 --> 00:06:55,667
I can't tell.

132
00:06:55,667 --> 00:06:58,708
We were attacked by an earth dragon.

133
00:06:58,708 --> 00:07:02,083
Asking us not to practise
any skill in this world is...

134
00:07:02,083 --> 00:07:04,542
Skills are dangerous.

135
00:07:04,542 --> 00:07:07,750
Please believe in my words.

136
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:11,375
But Yuri told us to practise our skills nonstop.

137
00:07:11,375 --> 00:07:14,417
-That's a dangerous mindset.
-There wouldn't be monsters in that place.

138
00:07:14,417 --> 00:07:16,375
Let's go camping.

139
00:07:16,375 --> 00:07:18,917
You're Hugo indeed.

140
00:07:18,917 --> 00:07:21,458
Okay.
We should go for outdoor activities happily.

141
00:07:21,458 --> 00:07:22,708
Yes.

142
00:07:24,625 --> 00:07:28,208
You must have
a good relationship with your friends.

143
00:07:29,042 --> 00:07:30,917
Talk to Natsume.

144
00:07:30,917 --> 00:07:32,250
Brother.

145
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:34,000
You should have told me you went to the canteen.

146
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,875
Why didn't you tell me?

147
00:07:36,875 --> 00:07:38,917
Sorry. What's going on?

148
00:07:38,917 --> 00:07:42,542
Those who joined
the off-campus education should gather now.

149
00:07:42,542 --> 00:07:47,167
To all 12 of you
who decided to join the off-campus education,

150
00:07:47,167 --> 00:07:52,292
please split yourselves into groups
for the activities in the mountains.

151
00:07:52,292 --> 00:07:57,708
Experiencing the habitat
of the monsters is one of the goals.

152
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:03,833
Only low-level monsters inhabit this mountain.

153
00:08:03,833 --> 00:08:05,708
Don't worry.

154
00:08:07,375 --> 00:08:12,542
Another goal is to collect herbs
and to learn the knowledge of the mountains.

155
00:08:12,542 --> 00:08:14,625
Draw a lot to decide on your group.

156
00:08:17,625 --> 00:08:20,083
Brother, which group are you in?

157
00:08:22,333 --> 00:08:24,833
No, don't be like that, Sue.

158
00:08:24,833 --> 00:08:28,333
Sue and I are in the same group.
Please guide me.

159
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:30,958
I'm in the same group as you too.

160
00:08:30,958 --> 00:08:32,500
Shun, which group are you in?

161
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:35,082
I'm in the same group as Teacher Olisa.

162
00:08:35,082 --> 00:08:36,957
In the same group as Hugo?

163
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:42,582
Please guide me.

164
00:08:42,582 --> 00:08:44,917
Mr. Schlain, it's my honour.

165
00:08:44,917 --> 00:08:46,375
Please guide me.

166
00:08:50,625 --> 00:08:56,750
Everyone, collect your own things
and start the activities. Dismiss.

167
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:01,667
Brother, goodbye for now.

168
00:09:01,667 --> 00:09:03,875
We are only apart for one day.
You're exaggerating it.

169
00:09:03,875 --> 00:09:06,083
Even one day is a big matter.

170
00:09:06,083 --> 00:09:09,417
Whenever I think about you
being in danger which I can't see,

171
00:09:09,417 --> 00:09:10,917
I can't sleep at night.

172
00:09:10,917 --> 00:09:12,333
I will be fine.

173
00:09:12,333 --> 00:09:17,500
Sue, just have a good chat with me tonight.

174
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,833
Shun.

175
00:09:18,833 --> 00:09:21,917
Identify your teammates tonight.

176
00:09:21,917 --> 00:09:25,917
If you find someone
using forbidden skills, tell me.

177
00:09:25,917 --> 00:09:28,333
Okay. I will remember that.

178
00:09:29,792 --> 00:09:32,875
It's better that I don't use
the identification skill.

179
00:09:33,958 --> 00:09:38,375
You should use this chance
to fix your relationship with Natsume.

180
00:09:38,375 --> 00:09:41,333
We're all reincarnations.
We can't be hating each other forever.

181
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,750
Yes.

182
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,875
Is Fei angry?

183
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:52,833
Companion monsters aren't allowed
to join off-campus educations?

184
00:09:52,833 --> 00:09:54,333
I think so.

185
00:09:54,333 --> 00:09:59,667
After all, this activity is
to test the students' independence.

186
00:09:59,667 --> 00:10:01,417
But I'm surprised.

187
00:10:01,417 --> 00:10:02,958
Why?

188
00:10:02,958 --> 00:10:05,208
You actually joined so obediently.

189
00:10:05,208 --> 00:10:10,667
I'm indeed a problematic student
who's always absent.

190
00:10:10,667 --> 00:10:13,667
Why are you always on leave?

191
00:10:13,667 --> 00:10:17,042
No matter how I ask,
you will say it's a secret, right?

192
00:10:17,042 --> 00:10:19,042
You're right.

193
00:10:19,042 --> 00:10:20,958
Is this the campsite?

194
00:10:20,958 --> 00:10:23,333
It seems we're earlier than expected.

195
00:10:23,333 --> 00:10:25,208
Let's start preparing.

196
00:10:25,208 --> 00:10:26,917
Okay.

197
00:10:26,917 --> 00:10:30,000
A man's physical strength is indeed good.

198
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:33,750
As a girl, it's tiring for me to follow up.

199
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:36,833
Your ability value should be quite high.

200
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:40,083
This can't be tough for you.

201
00:10:40,083 --> 00:10:44,583
Even if you know this,
you should pretend like you don't know.

202
00:10:44,583 --> 00:10:47,875
A good man should just greet me kindly.

203
00:10:47,875 --> 00:10:52,375
I don't want to be a henpecked man.

204
00:10:56,583 --> 00:11:00,250
Mr. Schlain, can you please hand it over to me?

205
00:11:05,333 --> 00:11:08,125
Okay, it's done.

206
00:11:08,125 --> 00:11:09,125
Thank you.

207
00:11:09,125 --> 00:11:12,792
No, I should thank you for your help.

208
00:11:12,792 --> 00:11:14,042
I'm sorry.

209
00:11:14,042 --> 00:11:17,875
Palton, status is irrelevant in school.

210
00:11:17,875 --> 00:11:20,250
