230
00:12:30,958 --> 00:12:34,750
Forget about the small potato.

231
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:36,667
How can you say he's a small potato?

232
00:12:40,958 --> 00:12:42,250
How annoying.

233
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:46,250
I wanted to get rid of you around here.

234
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:49,542
You're really in the way.

235
00:12:49,542 --> 00:12:53,333
This world exists for me to conquer it.

236
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:54,917
But there's someone who's equal

237
00:12:54,917 --> 00:12:57,917
or even better than me.
Do you think I can be reconciled to this?

238
00:12:57,917 --> 00:13:01,042
What are you talking about? Are you serious?

239
00:13:01,042 --> 00:13:03,250
Of course, I'm serious.

240
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:08,167
This is a dream world, where you can
be anything as long as you have the skill.

241
00:13:08,167 --> 00:13:12,708
This world exists because of me.

242
00:13:12,708 --> 00:13:17,458
But I don't need a person like you.

243
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:20,958
So, die.

244
00:13:24,542 --> 00:13:27,500
HUGO BAINT RENXANDT. LEVEL 31.

245
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:30,917
What's wrong? Are you shivering?

246
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,333
So powerful.

247
00:13:39,333 --> 00:13:42,417
Besides, he's working
very hard on obtaining skills.

248
00:13:43,208 --> 00:13:45,208
The trickiest part of all...

249
00:13:45,208 --> 00:13:47,000
is The Skill of The Emperor.

250
00:13:48,125 --> 00:13:51,500
I can resist the fear
under the pressure of authority.

251
00:13:51,500 --> 00:13:54,333
But the fact that
it can improve skills is horrifying.

252
00:13:54,333 --> 00:13:55,417
