00:14:14,375 --> 00:14:17,958
Do you think you can get out of this
after doing such things?

260
00:14:17,958 --> 00:14:22,208
Haven't I told you? I'm the future king.

261
00:14:22,208 --> 00:14:25,417
I can do whatever I want.

262
00:14:27,625 --> 00:14:29,542
King?

263
00:14:31,083 --> 00:14:33,875
I've planned beforehand.

264
00:14:33,875 --> 00:14:37,583
My subordinates are dealing with the rest.

265
00:14:37,583 --> 00:14:39,292
After dealing with you,

266
00:14:39,292 --> 00:14:41,750
I will release the monsters I brought along.

267
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,083
Monsters?

268
00:14:43,083 --> 00:14:46,833
Those are powerful monsters
that won't appear here.

269
00:14:46,833 --> 00:14:49,708
Poor Prince Shun, Teacher Olisa,

270
00:14:49,708 --> 00:14:55,375
and other students will be eaten by monsters.
Just like this.

271
00:14:55,375 --> 00:14:57,333
Next, I will beat the monsters

272
00:14:57,333 --> 00:15:01,500
for the justice of my comrades.
Then I shall go back alive.

273
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:05,125
Your horrible plan is going to be reported.

274
00:15:05,125 --> 00:15:07,667
Who's going to report on me?

275
00:15:07,667 --> 00:15:10,000
This isn't Japan.

276
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:13,333
Even if something is strange,
who would bring it up?

277
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:19,667
After committing a crime,
it won't be told to the world.

278
00:15:19,667 --> 00:15:22,708
You're abnormal.

279
00:15:22,708 --> 00:15:29,750
You're abnormal for obeying
the common sense of the previous world here.

280
00:15:31,792 --> 00:15:35,250
What a weak sword.

281
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,375
It's ridiculously weak.

282
00:15:39,917 --> 00:15:43,333
Where is the heroic gesture
when you defeated the earth dragon?

283
00:15:43,333 --> 00:15:45,125
Your Highness.

284
00:15:48,583 --> 00:15:51,875
I'm stronger after all.

285
00:15:51,875 --> 00:15:56,375
You were just lucky
when you defeated the earth dragon.

286
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:00,958
Goodbye forever.

287
00:16:00,958 --> 00:16:05,792
I will remember you.

288
00:16:11,250 --> 00:16:15,000
Natsume, you have gone too far.

289
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:17,500
It's you... Oka...

290
00:16:18,792 --> 00:16:22,167
All your subordinates have been caught.

291
00:16:22,167 --> 00:16:25,042
The monsters you brought along
have been destroyed too.

292
00:16:25,042 --> 00:16:26,875
What?

293
00:16:26,875 --> 00:16:31,250
I can't allow you to be
so out of control anymore.

294
00:16:40,292 --> 00:16:42,667
Is that the Magic of Wind?

295
00:16:43,708 --> 00:16:45,000
Let me go.

296
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,917
Activate ruler's power limitation.

297
00:16:46,917 --> 00:16:48,708
According to the ruler's request,

298
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:51,083
the special skill
of the ruler shall be activated.

299
00:16:51,083 --> 00:16:52,917
Do you agree?

300
00:16:55,125 --> 00:16:56,833
I agree.

301
00:16:58,083 --> 00:17:01,875
His ability values are decreasing.

302
00:17:01,875 --> 00:17:03,292
Even his skills are...

303
00:17:03,292 --> 00:17:06,041
What did you do to me?

304
00:17:06,041 --> 00:17:09,541
I reduced your ability values
and confiscated your skills.

305
00:17:09,541 --> 00:17:10,082
What?

306
00:17:10,083 --> 00:17:12,208
Shun, how's the identification result?

307
00:17:12,208 --> 00:17:14,333
All ability values are at 30.

308
00:17:14,333 --> 00:17:16,667
(n%I=W)
His skills are gone.

309
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:21,833
The world doesn't belong to you.

310
00:17:21,833 --> 00:17:23,125
Reflect on yourself.

311
00:17:23,125 --> 00:17:27,208
Besides, I suggest you
to live on as a normal person.

312
00:17:27,208 --> 00:17:30,958
My...

313
00:17:30,958 --> 00:17:32,208
Shun.

314
00:17:32,208 --> 00:17:35,667
Go help Teacher Olisa
and Palton with their injuries.

315
00:17:35,667 --> 00:17:36,917
Yes, the two of them...

316
00:17:36,917 --> 00:17:39,875
It's okay. They sustain only light injuries.

317
00:17:39,875 --> 00:17:43,917
After treatment, send them
to the hut at the bottom of the mountain.

318
00:17:43,917 --> 00:17:46,375
The off-campus education has ended.

319
00:17:47,792 --> 00:17:51,792
Did you really confiscate Hugo's skills?

320
00:17:51,792 --> 00:17:53,292
Haven't I told you?

321
00:17:53,292 --> 00:17:55,625
Skills are dangerous.

322
00:18:11,167 --> 00:18:13,458
Proficiency achieved a certain target.

323
00:18:13,458 --> 00:18:17,250
Visual enhancement upgraded to level 10.

324
00:18:17,250 --> 00:18:19,125
Conditions fulfilled.

325
00:18:19,125 --> 00:18:22,333
Since visual enhancement
is upgraded to level 10,

326
00:18:22,333 --> 00:18:22,958
Great!

327
00:18:22,958 --> 00:18:25,417
-telescopic sight is derived.
-Visual enhancement is at its highest level now.

328
00:18:25,417 --> 00:18:29,208
Besides, because of the highest level,
a new skill is derived as a reward.

329
00:18:29,208 --> 00:18:32,667
"TELESCOPIC SIGHT: ZOOM IN TO SEE DISTANT SCENERY."
It's so clear.

330
00:18:32,667 --> 00:18:36,042
It's a little ambiguous and unremarkable,

331
00:18:36,042 --> 00:18:38,208
but I should just activate it first.

332
00:18:38,208 --> 00:18:39,833
Come on. Activate!

333
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:45,000
This is awesome!

334
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,875
Sorry for saying you're unremarkable.

335
00:18:46,875 --> 00:18:49,875
Two fields of view appear at the same time.

336
00:18:49,875 --> 00:18:51,375
I'm confused.

337
00:18:51,375 --> 00:18:52,542
I'm just kidding.

338
00:18:52,542 --> 00:18:55,500
I have a clone now.

339
00:18:55,500 --> 00:18:58,542
It can be divided into two sides.

340
00:18:58,542 --> 00:19:02,500
The Sickle of Death is upgraded
from level two to three.

341
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:06,833
Vision field expansion
is upgraded to level three.

342
00:19:06,833 --> 00:19:10,750
Life is upgraded to level 10.

343
00:19:10,750 --> 00:19:12,708
Conditions fulfilled.

344
00:19:12,708 --> 00:19:18,208
Level-10 Life is upgraded
to level-one Bodily Life.

345
00:19:18,208 --> 00:19:20,583
The person in charge of body...

346
00:19:20,583 --> 00:19:23,125
What, the person in charge of information?

347
00:19:23,125 --> 00:19:26,167
Can I add the telescopic view to the Evil Eye?

348
00:19:27,250 --> 00:19:30,083
You're a genius.

349
00:19:30,083 --> 00:19:33,083
A genius can do anything, right?

350
00:19:33,083 --> 00:19:37,083
If I can use the Evil Eye from a distance,
it must be awesome.

351
00:19:37,083 --> 00:19:39,708
Great! The dream becomes bigger.

352
00:19:39,708 --> 00:19:43,542
If I decided to do that,
I must find a prey for an experiment.

353
00:19:43,542 --> 00:19:45,042
Investigate!

354
00:19:45,042 --> 00:19:47,417
Proficiency achieved a certain target.

355
00:19:47,417 --> 00:19:49,792
Investigation skill is upgraded to level 10.

356
00:19:49,792 --> 00:19:50,625
What?

357
00:19:50,625 --> 00:19:52,750
Even the investigation skill
is upgraded to the highest level.

358
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:55,583
I'm on the path to be the strongest.

359
00:19:55,583 --> 00:20:01,083
But wouldn't another skill
be derived from the investigation skill?

360
00:20:01,083 --> 00:20:06,917
So the identification skill doesn't evolve
nor has any derivative skills.

361
00:20:07,917 --> 00:20:10,208
No, it's okay.

362
00:20:10,208 --> 00:20:13,167
It's great enough to train
until the highest level.

363
00:20:13,167 --> 00:20:20,917
I thought a wise man would appear.

364
00:20:20,917 --> 00:20:24,333
But the end result is very disappointing.

365
00:20:27,583 --> 00:20:30,750
What? It's the rustling noise again.

366
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:34,083
Hey, what's that?

367
00:20:35,917 --> 00:20:37,250
What?

368
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:39,208
I think I hear a tinkle.

369
00:20:39,208 --> 00:20:41,583
It's surely not the rustling noise.

370
00:20:41,583 --> 00:20:45,167
Your request has been accepted by Admin D.

371
00:20:45,167 --> 00:20:46,417
Who's D?

372
00:20:46,417 --> 00:20:49,000
The skill, Wisdom, is being created.

373
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,167
Creation complete.

374
00:20:51,167 --> 00:20:52,958
Conditions fulfilled.

375
00:20:52,958 --> 00:20:55,750
Wisdom obtained.

376
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:56,875
-Identification skill and Wisdom are combined.
-What?

377
00:20:56,875 --> 00:20:58,292
-Identification skill and wisdom are combined.
-No, that's odd.

378
00:20:58,292 --> 00:21:00,250
-Proficiency achieved a certain target.
-This is just too odd.

379
00:21:00,250 --> 00:21:01,125
-Forbidden skill is upgraded
What's going on?

380
00:21:01,125 --> 00:21:02,250
-from level seven to eight.
-How did this happen?

381
00:21:02,250 --> 00:21:03,292
-Condition fulfilled.
-What should I do?

382
00:21:03,292 --> 00:21:06,500
-The title, The Ruler of Wisdom, is obtained.
-Calm down. Take a deep breath.

383
00:21:13,417 --> 00:21:16,833
This is obviously an abnormal situation.

384
00:21:16,833 --> 00:21:18,375
Abnormal...

385
00:21:18,375 --> 00:21:20,583
Right, abnormal.

386
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:25,292
I thought I was obtaining skills
according to the rules of this world.

387
00:21:25,292 --> 00:21:27,625
I thought I was following the stream.

388
00:21:27,625 --> 00:21:31,000
Just like the life in a game.

389
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:33,167
Because it's odd to have weird things

390
00:21:33,167 --> 00:21:37,042
like skills and ability values in real life.

391
00:21:37,042 --> 00:21:41,542
Your request has been accepted by Admin D.

392
00:21:41,542 --> 00:21:46,333
This sounds like someone is watching me,

393
00:21:46,333 --> 00:21:50,250
someone is creating skills
that match my complaints.

394
00:21:50,250 --> 00:21:52,083
If that's really the case,

395
00:21:52,083 --> 00:21:54,583
someone who's managing may be around.

396
00:21:54,583 --> 00:21:58,167
If someone is watching
the development of this world,

397
00:21:58,167 --> 00:22:01,583
isn't this person like God?

398
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:04,833
Then this is not a game world,

399
00:22:04,833 --> 00:22:09,583
but a game, which is managed by an admin.

400
00:22:11,833 --> 00:22:16,667
That means I'm just one of the characters.

401
00:22:17,625 --> 00:22:21,750
Am I considered as alive?

402
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:23,458
This is scary.

403
00:22:24,833 --> 00:22:28,667
What should I do from now on?

404
00:22:28,667 --> 00:22:30,625
What should I do?

405
00:22:35,083 --> 00:22:36,917
What a joke.

406
00:22:36,917 --> 00:22:39,500
What does it mean I've gone too far?

407
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:44,750
I must get my revenge on that evil elf.

408
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:50,125
I want to destroy everything you cherish.

409
00:22:50,125 --> 00:22:53,458
This world belongs to me.

410
00:22:56,292 --> 00:22:58,625
Let me give you a hand.

411
00:23:02,583 --> 00:23:04,958
Who are you?

412
00:23:04,958 --> 00:23:07,708
Because you're a reincarnation,

413
00:23:07,708 --> 00:23:10,792
I'm willing to help you.

414
00:23:10,792 --> 00:23:14,167
What reincarnation are you talking about?

415
00:23:19,833 --> 00:23:21,708
Forget it.

416
00:23:21,708 --> 00:23:25,542
It doesn't matter who you are.

417
00:23:25,542 --> 00:23:28,208
As long as I can get my revenge,

418
00:23:28,208 --> 00:23:31,833
I don't care if you're a devil or a human.

419
00:23:31,833 --> 00:23:36,333
Okay. I shall accept your offer.

420
00:23:36,333 --> 00:23:39,000
SO I'M A SPIDER, SO WHAT?
NEXT EPISODE: I WILL DIE

421
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:41,458
STAY TUNED

